  },
  {
    "row": 95,
    "rowsha": "CruvtzzBtAPacqGoq9iZnTXh0goMcpb/8NQ0/W1BZ50=",
    "originContent": "- **External T5 input** — connect pre-computed T5 embeddings (3584 dim) from another encoder node",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
